      "PACIFIC\nPACIFIC AIR LINES\nTIMETABLE\nEFFECTIVE APRIL 30, 1967",
      "PACIFIC ANNOUNCES\nNEW 727 JET SERVICE AND\nNEW JET COACH FARES*\nWITHIN CALIFORNIA AND NEVADA\nSAN JOSE-LOS ANGELES\nNON STOP\nSAN JOSE-LAS VEGAS\nNON STOP\nSAN FRANCISCO -HOLLYWOOD/BURBANK\nNON STOP\nSAN FRANCISCO-EUREKA\nNON STOP\nSAN FRANCISCO-SANTA BARBARA\nONE STOP\nSAN FRANCISCO-FRESNO\nNON STOP\nSAN FRANCISCO-BAKERSFIELD\nONE STOP\nLOS ANGELES-MONTEREY\nONE STOP\nLOS ANGELES-FRESNO\nONE STOP\n†HOLLYWOOD/BURBANK-LAS VEGAS\nNON STOP\nHOLLYWOOD/BURBANK-EUREKA\nONE STOP\n$13.50\n$23.81\n$13.50\n$17.14\n$19.04\n$12.58\n$19.04\n$20.00\n$16.19\n$14.50\n$30.64\nMEDFORD\nCRESCENT CITY\nCHICE\nSANTA ROSA\nLAKE TANUE\nSAN FRANCISCO\nOAKLAN\nSAN JOSE\n_ SALINA\nSAN LUIS OBISPO\n—PASO ROBLES\nSANTA MARIA\nVANDENBERG A.F.B.\nSANTA BARBARA\nOXNARD — VENTURA\n...AND THERE'S EVEN MORE!\nSee schedules for additional 727 Jet and new Prop-Jet service to these and\nLUS ANGELES\nLONG BEACH\nother cities.\nMORE JETS MORE SERVICE LOW JET COACH FARES SAN DEODO\nMore people fly Pacific to more Pacific Coast cities than any other airline.\nJET-PROP\nAnd now... more reasons than ever!\n*Jet coach fares effective April 30 subject to CAB approval.\n†Hollywood/Burbank-Las Vegas route subject to CAB approval."
